name: Cute Kitty Cat Dress Up
description:
Do you love cute cat? Take care of your own kitten and dress Cute Kitty Cat up! Design her new look and choose from the unlimited selection of dresses, shoes, and a whole lot of accessories. Show off your creative style by mixing and matching clothes and accessories to create new looks. Exciting fun and addicting dress up game.

HOW TO PLAY:

Tap the screen and start dressing your Cute Kitty Cat.

- Fashionable Clothes and Accessories
- Awesome Backgrounds
- Cool Sounds

Challenge Your Friends and See Who Creates the Trendiest and Fashionable Looks for your kittens!

EXCITING FUN!!

Download ‘Cute Kitty Cat Dress Up’ now and have some fun.
